\s HARI IKINTU CAMYE KIBA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Har’ikintu camye kiba, ku bana b’Imana ibihe vyose, nico catumye bitwa abahizi, ibigatanya bakabirya b\bd*\bd u\bd*\bd tsima\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.N’ukwizera \bd*\bd Isezerano \bd*\bd n’ukwizera ivyo utabona bigaragaza umuhizi./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ivyo bituma umuntu, yihanganir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ibimugerageza; ivyo bituma umuntu, ashikir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit isezerano yasezeranijwe\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.Akitwa umuhizi akitw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit uwanesheje, akambikwa igitsibo akambikwa ubwiza./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Har’ikintu camye kiba, ku bana b’Isumba ibiriho vyose, n’ukudacobogora mu rugendo\bd*\bd , n’ukudacobogora mu kwizera ./.\bd*\bd Bizer’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ibitaboneka mu nzira zifunganye no mu mwiza mwinshi cane./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ivyo bituma umuntu, yihanganir’ ibimugerageza; ivyo bituma umuntu, ashikir’ isezerano yasezeranijwe ./.Akitwa umuhizi akitw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit uwanesheje, akambikwa igitsibo akambikwa ubwiza./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Har’ikintu camye kiba, ku bana b’Aburahamu sogokuruza n’ukutaraba ku vy’isi y’umwiza, n’ukutarya ku giti c’ubumenyi\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Buzuy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ukwihangana, buzuye ukwizera, buzuye ivyizigiro./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ivyo bituma umuntu, yihanganir’ ibimugerageza; ivyo bituma umuntu, ashikir’ isezerano yasezeranijwe ./.Akitwa umuhizi akitw’ uwanesheje, akambikwa igitsibo akambikwa ubwiza./.\bdit*
